@{b}Signetics Mnemonic:@{ub}             ADDI,r   v
@{b}CALM Mnemonic:@{ub}                  ADD|ADDC reg,#imm
@{b}IEEE-694 Mnemonic@{ub}               ADD|ADDC reg,#imm
@{b}Binary Code:@{ub}                    $84-$87

